98
00:12:28,515 --> 00:12:29,714
         -[inaudible].          

99
00:12:31,718 --> 00:12:34,619
     -Hey, what's up there?     

100
00:12:37,591 --> 00:12:40,992
    A secret passageway for     
      spying on the monks?      

