MARA: You know, the 
    funny thin about Castle     

163
00:18:35,782 --> 00:18:39,317
 Vladislas is that nobody ever  
    says anything about it.     

164
00:18:39,319 --> 00:18:40,751
         -You're right.         

165
00:18:40,753 --> 00:18:43,955
  Nobody's mentioned it once.   

166
00:18:43,957 --> 00:18:44,856
      LILLIAN:      
      Let's see if we can       

167
00:18:44,858 --> 00:18:46,224
     get inside the castle.     

168
00:18:46,226 --> 00:18:47,892
     I've never been inside     
          one before.           

169
00:18:47,894 --> 00:18:49,527
 -Come on, we can't right now.  

170
00:18:49,529 --> 00:18:50,228
     It's getting too dark.     

171
00:18:50,230 --> 00:18:51,596
     We've got to get back.     

